**Privacy Policy for AOTY Rating Overlay**

This extension does not collect, store, or transmit any personal data.

The extension operates entirely within your browser and only runs on Album of the Year (albumoftheyear.org). It uses your existing logged-in session to retrieve your ratings directly from the website and display them on album pages.

No data is sent to any external servers, and no user information is tracked or shared.

